Arcana
------
Minimal plain JS UI controls.

Spectrum
--------
A minimal range input control.

Sample CSS
---------
.spectrum {
    position: relative;
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 6px 0;
}

.spectrum .track {
    width: inherit;
    height: 8px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    background: #CCC;
}

.spectrum .thumb {
    position: absolute;
    width: 14px;
    height: 14px;
    border-radius: 7px;
    top: 3px;
    background: #333;
}

.spectrum .fill {
    height: inherit;
    border-radius: inherit;
    background: #333;
}
